title: Are Ties Good For the NFL?
itunes:title: Are Ties Good For the NFL?
description:
The Good Morning Football Crew reacts to some of the most interesting games from week 2 of the NFL season and looks ahead to week 3 with Josh Gordon signing with the Patriots. The gang also discusses Carson Wentz’ return. Lastly, Kay Adams, Nate Burleson, Peter Schrager, and Kyle Brandt give you their underappreciated storylines. Be sure to check in every Wednesday to the GMFB podcast! Like, share, subscribe!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
